articles.title: Sen. Booker: 'All Americans should be concerned right now'
articles.description: Sen. Cory Booker reflects on the repercussions that follow the U.S. killing Iranian general Qassem Soleimani.

articles.title: At least 12 million acres burned in Australia wildfires
articles.description: The wildfires in Australia are worsening, and at least 12 million acres have been burned. NBC News' Janis Mackey Frayer reports from Southeastern Australia on whether the weather will improve.
